// Nested method call as method-call argument. Both inner and outer
// need explicit continuations (here both `.`). The desugaring runs
// at each level independently, so the resulting AST has two nested
// SendSyncs each prepending their own method-name StringLiteral --
// equivalent to hand-written `x!?("y", a!?("z", b).).`.
new x, a, b in {
  x!y(a!z(b).).
}
